column2: SELECT id AS up_id,  ra AS up_ra,  dec AS up_dec FROM MYDB.DRPALLV2_#_#_IDRADEC  CREATE TABLE #tmp (   up_id varchar(#),   objid bigint ) INSERT INTO #tmp EXEC spGetNeighbors #  INSERT INTO MYDB.DRPALLVCR SELECT a.id, t.objid as matched_id, s.specObjID, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, a.ra, a.dec, s.z, g.spectrotype, g.subclass, p.cModelAbsMag_u, p.cModelAbsMag_g, p.cModelAbsMag_r,   p.cModelAbsMag_i, p.cModelAbsMag_z, p.logMass_median, e.EW_Hb_#, e.EW_Hb_#_Err, e.Flux_Hb_#,   e.Flux_Hb_#_Err, e.EW_OIII_#, e.EW_OIII_#_Err, e.Flux_OIII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#_Err, e.EW_Ha_#, e.EW_Ha_#_Err,  e.Flux_Ha_#,   e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.EW_NII_#, e.EW_NII_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_Err, zo.p_mg,   zo.p_el_debiased, zo.p_cs_debiased, zm.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_smooth_debiased, zm.t0#_bar_a0#_bar_debiased, zm.t0#_spiral_a0#_spiral_debiased, zm.t0#_bulge_prominence_a1#_no_bulge_debiased, zm.t0#_bulge_prominence_a1#_just_noticeable_debiased, zm.t0#_bulge_prominence_a1#_obvious_debiased, zm.t0#_bulge_prominence_a1#_dominant_debiased, zm.t0#_odd_a1#_yes_debiased, zm.t0#_rounded_a1#_completely_round_debiased, zm.t0#_rounded_a1#_in_between_debiased,   zm.t0#_rounded_a1#_cigar_shaped_debiased, zm.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_tight_debiased, zm.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_medium_debiased, zm.t1#_arms_winding_a3#_loose_debiased FROM #tmp t   JOIN MYDB.DRPALLV2_#_#_IDRADEC a ON t.up_id = a.id   JOIN specobj s ON s.bestobjid=t.objid   JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust p on p.specObjID = s.specObjID   JOIN galSpecInfo g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID   JOIN emissionLinesPort e on e.specObjID = s.specObjID   JOIN zooSpec zo on zo.specobjid = s.specObjID   JOIN zoo2MainSpecz zm on zm.specobjid = s.specObjID WHERE s.class = &&&
